      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54-powered legend. The 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a double VANOS system that remains in peak operating condition. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings throughout. The exterior retains its factory luster, while the interior shows no bolster wear or upholstery fatigue. This vehicle has received comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a full cooling system overhaul, making it a mechanically pure, turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
